main event: Several observers noticed a flashing alarm and light in the sky, attributed to an object moving at high speed and changing directions erratically.
interesting points: The object was observed moving in a zigzag course., The observation lasted approximately 2 minutes., Ground trace was found., The event was recorded on a project 10073 record card from Project Blue Book., The object was assumed to be a meteorite.
sighted object: an unidentified object traveling at high speed
